OL,3,CHead of Southport attacker's former
OL,4,Cschool felt 'sense of dread'
OL,6,FThe head teacher of the Southport
OL,7,Fattacker's former school has told a
OL,8,Fpublic inquiry she had a "visceral
OL,9,Fsense of dread" that he would do
OL,10,Fsomething.
OL,12,FJoanne Hodson, head of The Acorns
OL,13,FSchool in Ormskirk, which the killer
OL,14,Fattended after he was excluded from
OL,15,Fthe Range High School, said she felt
OL,16,Flike he was "building up to something".
