OL,3,CHead of Southport attacker's former
OL,4,Cschool felt 'sense of dread'
OL,6,FShe said: "I felt like something was
OL,7,Fgoing to happen and there was a level
OL,8,Fof agitation with direct challenges to
OL,9,Fstaff, the way he was with other
OL,10,Fpupils. I felt like every day it was
OL,11,Fbuilding and building and building."
OL,13,FSitting at Liverpool Town Hall, the
OL,14,FSouthport Inquiry heard the killer,
OL,15,Freferred to as AR, was permanently
OL,16,Fexcluded from the Range, in Formby,
OL,17,Fafter admitting taking knives into
OL,18,Fschool in October 2019.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@dO]
