OL,6,FThe killer, then aged 17, killed Bebe
OL,7,FKing, six, Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven,
OL,8,Fand Alice da Silva Aguiar, nine, and
OL,9,Fattempted to murder 10 others at a
OL,10,FTaylor Swift-themed dance class in
OL,11,FSouthport on 19 July 2024.
OL,13,FMs Hodson described a "memorable"
OL,14,Ffirst meeting with the teenager at his
OL,15,Fadmissions meeting for the Acorns,
OL,16,Fwhen she asked him why he had taken a
OL,17,Fknife in to his former school.
OL,26,@uD@WOUuD@aO]
