OL,3,CHead of Southport attacker's former
OL,4,Cschool felt 'sense of dread'
OL,6,FShe said: "He looked me in the eyes
OL,7,Fand said 'to use it'. This is the only
OL,8,Ftime in my career that a pupil has
OL,9,Fsaid this to me or behaved in a manner
OL,10,Fso devoid of any remorse.
OL,12,F"What also surprised me was that AR's
OL,13,Fparents did not flinch at this
OL,14,Fcomment."
OL,16,FShe said the parents believed he had
OL,17,Ftaken the knife in to school as a
OL,18,Fresponse to being bullied.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUvD@IO]
