OL,3,CHead of Southport attacker's former
OL,4,Cschool felt 'sense of dread'
OL,6,FShe told the inquiry: "He saw himself
OL,7,Fand his parents saw him as the victim
OL,8,Fof the incident rather than the
OL,9,Fperpetrator."
OL,11,FShe said AR was the "most unusual"
OL,12,Fpupil she had experienced during her
OL,13,Fcareer.
OL,15,FIn a statement, she said: "There was a
OL,16,Fsinister undertone and it was
OL,17,Fdifficult to build rapport. He had no
OL,18,Frespect for authority and generally a
OL,19,Flack of respect of other pupils and
OL,20,Fstaff.
OL,26,@nD@WOUqD@MO]sD@UOUsD@bO]wD@[OU
